<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ١٠٠ ... سُورَةُ العَادِيَاتِ ... آياتها ١١ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْعَادِيَاتِ ضَبْحًا}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالخَيْلِ الجَارِيَةِ فِي سَبِيلِ اللهِ، حِينَ يَظْهَرُ صَوْتُهَا مِنْ سُرْعَةِ عَدْوِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَالْمُورِيَاتِ قَدْحًا}</span> ... فَالمُوقِدَاتِ بِحَوَافِرِهَا النَّارَ مِنْ شِدَّةِ عَدْوِهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَالْمُغِيرَاتِ صُبْحًا}</span> ... فَالخَيْلِ الَّتِي تُغِيرُ وَتُبَاغِتُ العَدُوَّ صَبَاحًا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَثَرْنَ}</span> ... فَهَيَّجْنَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَقْعًا}</span> ... غُبَارًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَوَسَطْنَ بِهِ جَمْعًا}</span> ... فَتَوَسَّطْنَ بِرُكْبَانِهِنَّ جُمُوعَ الأَعْدَاءِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَكَنُودٌ}</span> ... لَجَحُودٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَشَهِيدٌ}</span> ... لَمُقِرٌّ عَلَى جُحُودِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْخَيْرِ}</span> ... المَالِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُعْثِرَ}</span> ... أُثِيرَ، وَأُخْرِجَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَحُصِّلَ}</span> ... اُسْتُخْرِجَ، وَأُبْرِزَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>